---
import Layout from '../components/layout/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - Zachary King"
  description="20+ years in B2B sales, now building AI-native GTM systems for startups. Not just strategy decks. Not just playbooks. Actual systems that run on AI."
>
  <Section id="about-hero" background="white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="mb-8">About</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
          I've spent 20+ years in B2B sales â€” from early-stage startups to running Asia for a $900M adtech company. I've launched markets, built teams, and closed enterprise deals across three continents.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Now I work exclusively with startups building AI-native GTM systems.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Not just strategy decks. Not just playbooks. Actual systems that run on AI and keep working after I leave.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
          I'm deep in the weeds with Claude, automations, and agent workflows. I use AI daily in my own work and I build it into everything I deliver to clients.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-6 my-8">
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
            If your GTM isn't leveraging AI yet, you're already behind.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
          I work with product-obsessed founders who want sales without killing the founder vibe. Startups who've proven the product works and now need to structure growth without hiring a full-time VP Sales.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
          If that sounds like you, let's talk.
        </p>

        <div class="text-center">
          <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" size="lg">
            Book a Call
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>
